title: Lil Mo Interview and More
itunes:title: Lil Mo Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had Lil Mo stopped by and spoke about her toxic relationship, Opioid addiction, new music and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a reporter who quit her job on air after finding out she won the lottery but only for 5,000 and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
